trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"></xref> objects that are used by data-bound controls such as <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"></xref> and <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField"> </xref> objekter som brukes av databundet Kontroller eksempel <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView"> </xref> og <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The DataControlFieldCollection class represents a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> objects used by data-bound controls to specify how their child controls are presented.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DataControlFieldCollection representerer en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objekter som brukes av databundet kontroller til å angi hvordan de underordnede kontrollene presenteres.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: The DataControlFieldCollection class derives from <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>, an abstract base collection class used specifically to store <xref:System.Web.UI.IStateManager> objects.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DataControlFieldCollection er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>, en abstrakt base Samlingsklasse brukes spesifikt for å lagre <xref:System.Web.UI.IStateManager>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.IStateManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection> object influences the behavior of a DataControlFieldCollection object.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>objektet påvirker virkemåten til et objekt for DataControlFieldCollection.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> objects that are dynamically added to the collection will be re-added to the control when state is restored.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objekter som er dynamisk legges til i samlingen er lagt til på nytt til kontrollen når gjenopprettes.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: This means that a field needs to be added, removed, or changed just once instead of on each postback, as most collection types in ASP.NET require.
trans-unit.target: Dette betyr at et felt må legges til, fjerne eller endre bare én gang i stedet for hver tilbakesending som krever at de fleste samlingstyper i ASP.NET.

trans-unit.source: (The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> class implements the <xref:System.Web.UI.IStateManager> interface, which enables it to store its state in ASP.NET view state.
trans-unit.target: (Det <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>klasse implementerer den <xref:System.Web.UI.IStateManager>grensesnittet som gjør det mulig å lagre tilstanden i ASP.NET visningsstatus.</xref:System.Web.UI.IStateManager> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: ) Use the DataControlFieldCollection class to programmatically manage a set of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> objects.
trans-unit.target: ) Bruk DataControlFieldCollection-klasse for å programmatisk administrere et sett med <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: Note that it is more common to define these fields declaratively.
trans-unit.target: Merk at det er flere vanlig til å definere disse feltene deklarativt.

trans-unit.source: You can add, insert, and remove <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> objects using the appropriate methods of the DataControlFieldCollection class.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til, insert og fjerne <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objekter ved hjelp av passende metoder av DataControlFieldCollection klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: To programmatically retrieve <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> objects from a collection, use one of following methods: - Use the indexer to get a single <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> object from the collection using array notation.
trans-unit.target: Hente programmatisk <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objekter fra en samling, bruker du én av følgende metoder:-Bruk indekserer til å få én <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objektet fra samlingen matrise notasjon.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>

trans-unit.source: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetEnumerator%2A> method to create a <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>-implemented object, which can then be used to get items from the collection.
trans-unit.target: -Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>metode for å opprette en <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>-implementert objektet, som kan brukes til å hente elementer fra samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Count%2A> property specifies the total number of items in the collection, and is commonly used to determine the upper bound of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Count%2A>egenskapen angir antall elementer i samlingen, og brukes vanligvis til å finne den øvre grensen for samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can add items to and remove items from the collection using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection.Add%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection.Insert%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection.Remove%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection.RemoveAt%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til elementer og Fjern elementene i samlingen ved hjelp av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection.Add%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection.Insert%2A>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection.Remove%2A>, og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection.RemoveAt%2A>metoder.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection.RemoveAt%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection.Remove%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection.Insert%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlFieldCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you are using the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> control, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> objects that are automatically created (for example, when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.AutoGenerateColumns%2A> property is `true`) are not stored in the publicly accessible fields collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du bruker den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView>kontroll, den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objekter som opprettes automatisk (for eksempel når den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.AutoGenerateColumns%2A>egenskapen `true`) ikke er lagret i den allment tilgjengelige feltsamlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView.AutoGenerateColumns%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DetailsView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.GridView>

trans-unit.source: You can only access and manipulate <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField> objects that are not automatically generated.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bare tilgang til og behandle <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>objekter som ikke er automatisk generert.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataControlField>
